  "body": "This is a list of visual and experience bugs for the text input area in chat:\r\n\r\n- [ ] **Input area doesn’t grow with long messages zpl.io/brN1Xre. (High prio)**\r\n<img width=\"691\" alt=\"captura de pantalla 2018-09-17 a la s 10 16 38 a m\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37297779/45612283-d51fea00-ba62-11e8-87e2-3113476e7ced.png\">\r\nSee how input fields grow >> zpl.io/brN1Xre (Zeplin)\r\n\r\n- [ ] Send button enabled styles are missing (blue) \r\n<img width=\"696\" alt=\"captura de pantalla 2018-09-17 a la s 10 18 20 a m\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37297779/45612559-a1918f80-ba63-11e8-8073-f73c4fe0040a.png\">\r\n\r\n- [ ] Review Send button disabled styles (grey) \r\n- [ ] Focus should be on input field when joining a new chat \r\n- [ ] Input area height should be 68px \r\n- [ ] Review color of \"Type a message” label \r\n- [ ] \"Type a message” label, send button and cursor are not aligned at the middle to the input box\r\n<img width=\"694\" alt=\"captura de pantalla 2018-09-17 a la s 10 20 05 a m\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37297779/45612548-8d4d9280-ba63-11e8-93e8-c5e449669716.png\">\r\n\r\nDesigns in Zeplin >> zpl.io/aXGDvmE\r\n",
